reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 2, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great phone protection. Durable. Good value.
reviews.reviewText: It took a while to figure out how to get this on, but I have been very happy with it ever since. It is so much more durable than my last phone case and I love the double layered protection of the hard inner case and the softer outer case. I liked that it came with the screen protector so I didn't have to order it separately. It's easy to clean - I just take a wet wipe to it and it's good as new. It has covers over the charging and headphone ports so dust and other debris doesn't get it and I love playing with those covers, fidgeting with them, and they have not torn or come loose at all. The one drawback is how deep the opening is for the finger scanner - sometimes I have to do the finger scan multiple times because the angle is off - but it is a worthwhile annoyance for an otherwise great phone case.
